OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779181629
OL,3,CInside the hospital that has abolished
OL,4,C'corridor care'
OL,6,FITV News Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,7,FBarry has been given exclusive access
OL,8,Fto Watford General Hospital, once
OL,9,Fdubbed one of the worst-performing
OL,10,Fhospitals on 'corridor care', to see
OL,11,Fhow they've eradicated the problem
OL,13,FThe corridors of the A&E department at
OL,14,FWatford General Hospital in
OL,15,FHertfordshire were once lined with
OL,16,Fdozens of patients, waiting hours, or
OL,17,Feven days, for a bed on a ward.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779181629
OL,3,CInside the hospital that has abolished
OL,4,C'corridor care'
OL,6,FA few years ago, there would regularly
OL,7,Fbe up to 28 patients left on trolleys
OL,8,Fin the crowded corridors, seven days a
OL,9,Fweek.
OL,11,FBut today, the hospital's hallways are
OL,12,Fclear and quiet.
OL,14,FIn recent months, there have been no
OL,15,Fcases of so-called 'corridor care',
OL,16,Fdespite record demand this winter.
OL,18,F"The number one thing that we've
OL,19,Fchanged here is the culture - the
OL,20,Fculture of accepting," chief nurse
OL,21,FKelly McGovern told ITV News.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779181629
OL,3,CInside the hospital that has abolished
OL,4,C'corridor care'
OL,6,FMs McGovern said 'corridor care' had
OL,7,Fbecome normalised, but now there's
OL,8,Fbeen a shift in mindset and staff aim
OL,9,Fto treat every patient like their own
OL,10,Ffamily member.
OL,12,F"It's actually soul-destroying to be
OL,13,Fnursing in a corridor, so we've
OL,14,Fallowed our staff to say it's not okay
OL,15,Fand we won't continue to do it,"
OL,16,Fexplained Ms McGovern.
OL,18,FThe hospital has managed to improve
OL,19,FA&E waiting times, moving from 102nd
OL,20,Fin the NHS league tables in 2022, to
OL,21,Fnow being in the top 10.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779181629
OL,3,CInside the hospital that has abolished
OL,4,C'corridor care'
OL,6,FGary Carmont, 76, has diabetes and
OL,7,Fregularly needs to visit the hospital.
OL,9,F"I was one of those patients in the
OL,10,Fcorridor. It was cold and it was very
OL,11,Fnoisy, because it wasn't equipped," Mr
OL,12,FCarmont told ITV News.
OL,14,F"The nurses did a good job, but it's
OL,15,Fmuch more organised now."
OL,17,FWhen nurse EJ Llamas arrived to work
OL,18,Fat Watford General Hospital from the
OL,19,FPhilippines, he was shocked at the NHS
OL,20,Fhe found.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@cO]vD@AOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779181629
OL,3,CInside the hospital that has abolished
OL,4,C'corridor care'
OL,6,FTreating patients in corridors was so
OL,7,Fdemoralising for him, he even
OL,8,Fconsidered leaving the profession.
OL,10,F"It was draining," Mr Llamas told ITV
OL,11,FNews.
OL,13,F"When you see patients suffering, I
OL,14,Fwasn't satisfied. I was giving them
OL,15,Ftreatment, but not the holistic care
OL,16,FI'm meant to give."
OL,18,FData analysis has played a big part in
OL,19,Fthe hospital's success.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@RO]uD@AOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
