PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779181629
OL,3,CInside the hospital that has abolished
OL,4,C'corridor care'
OL,6,FThey now have a control room with
OL,7,Ffloor-to-ceiling screens displaying
OL,8,Freal-time data on patients and bed
OL,9,Favailability.
OL,11,FThey have even borrowed techniques
OL,12,Ffrom Heathrow Airport to transform how
OL,13,Fpatients flow through the hospital.
OL,15,F"What you can see all around me are
OL,16,Fscreens showing real-time information
OL,17,Fthat track the patients' journey
OL,18,Fthrough our hospital," explained
OL,19,FRachel Thorman, chief operating
OL,20,Fofficer at the West Hertfordshire
OL,21,FTeaching Hospitals NHS Trust.
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779181629
OL,3,CInside the hospital that has abolished
OL,4,C'corridor care'
OL,6,F"We can match up the patients that
OL,7,Fneed a bed with the beds that we're
OL,8,Fgot coming available."
OL,10,FBut the secret to tackling corridor
OL,11,Fcare has not just been about changes
OL,12,Fwithin the hospital walls.
OL,14,FThe trust has teamed up with other
OL,15,Fparts of the health system, like the
OL,16,Fambulance service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779181629
OL,3,CInside the hospital that has abolished
OL,4,C'corridor care'
OL,6,FWhen ambulance crews have a suspected
OL,7,Fstroke patient, they can use iPads to
OL,8,Fvideo call doctors based at the
OL,9,Fhospital to help remotely diagnose
OL,10,Fthem, so that they can be fast-tracked
OL,11,Fto the right specialist team, avoiding
OL,12,Fany delays in A&E.
OL,14,FThe government has promised to
OL,15,Feradicate 'corridor care" in England
OL,16,Fby 2029.
OL,18,FThe Department of Health has pledged
OL,19,Fto deploy "expert teams" to the worst-
OL,20,Faffected hospitals, to provide support
OL,21,Fand leadership.
OL,26,@wD@YO]{D@KOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779181629
OL,3,CInside the hospital that has abolished
OL,4,C'corridor care'
OL,6,FIn March 2026, NHS England published a
OL,7,Fdefinition of 'corridor care' for the
OL,8,Ffirst time to allow trusts to begin
OL,9,Fcollecting data on the problem, which
OL,10,Fis due to be published later this
OL,11,Fmonth.
OL,13,FThe teams at Watford General Hospital
OL,14,Fare optimistic that others can learn
OL,15,Ffrom what they've achieved.
OL,17,F"It can be done. We've gone from being
OL,18,Fone of the worst in the country to
OL,19,Fhaving the highest number of extra
OL,20,Fbeds," Ms McGovern said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
